highlights.text: Sleep Token has the most spots on Viral Songs Global. “Gethsemane” is the highest at #49.
“Love Me Not” by Ravyn Lenae has been on Viral Songs Global the longest, at 103 days straight.
“Pendampingmu #TahtaHatiku” by Shabrina Leanor is the highest new entry on Viral Songs Global at #2.
“QUE HACES” by Becky G and Manuel Turizo is the biggest gainer on Viral Songs Global, up 10 spots at #73.
